As used in KRS 164.810 to 164.870, the following terms shall have, unless the context shall otherwise indicate, the following meanings:
"University of Louisville" means the university which is situated in a city of the first class, and which has heretofore constituted a municipal university within the meaning and application of KRS 165.010 et seq.;
"Council" means the Council on Postsecondary Education in Kentucky.
